external_knowledge:
- 'Good quality' refers to samples that do not have any issues or defects; 
- 'Chemical analysis' involves analyzing the chemical composition of a sample; 
- 'Civil project' refers to projects related to infrastructure or construction; 
- 'Quality engineer' is a role responsible for ensuring the quality of projects or processes.

sql:
SELECT s.sample_id, s.sample_taken_date, sa.analysis_id, sa.analysis_date
FROM samples AS s
JOIN sample_analysis AS sa ON s.sample_id = sa.sample_id;
